<br>
Warriors are incredibly underpowered now, once hybrids start getting Archetype AA skills (and even before it, with thier new spells and weapons / armor), Warriors become dead weight in a group, because one could simply get a Ranger who can buff, snare, nuke, DoT, and tank as well as us.<br>
<br>
And gear...it's not so much that I feel bad about taking things that has good stats for other classes that I won't make use of, so much as the fact that we have to COMPETE with those classes for almost every piece of equipment we get, then they can turn around and get a class specific piece to replace it within weeks.<br>
<br>
